{"tid":1448034,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今次絕對係好機會收哂班藍絲皮","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:21:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:41:31.000Z","uid":209700,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bee446ff714c3206b26911b6e33fa8a8a9319dd1","tid":1448034,"uid":209700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:21:28.000Z","msg":"一定要大肆宣傳示威者當中有大量狗混入<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n效果一：佢地會開始懷疑一直以來所謂既暴徒會唔會就係因為佢地支持開既黑警<br />\n<br />\n就算冇乜用 都可以造成對家一定既混亂 唔敢亂屌示威者 廢是屌錯黑警<br />\n<br />\n效果二：日後所有勇武既衝擊行為可以歸咎哂班鬼到<br />\n<br />\n等文宣出黎之後<br />\n<br />\n希望大家一定要煲大依件事佢！"},{"pid":"59815dc6d9a036fe07dfe821086ca95f73d0e8dc","tid":1448034,"uid":209700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:22:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"130b43ae960222362bce0e94555719916d5e8762","tid":1448034,"uid":209700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:23:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2b7941abcfc37fc1c350df83a6c052f2f74a6c2","tid":1448034,"uid":209700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:25:40.000Z","msg":"推啊！"},{"pid":"91eb550556b98634c1be46ba2749b524d49a826b","tid":1448034,"uid":209700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:25:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">721！</span></span></span>"},{"pid":"b14479ff51b523764efe4c4aabb73c7109323c92","tid":1448034,"uid":112457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:29:56.000Z","msg":"推阿"},{"pid":"60b93c00b716b05b7fbe4640f099f033c33527cf","tid":1448034,"uid":248394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:32:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e3700e388e79277ef701df3c09c9c2d1c3cfe92b","tid":1448034,"uid":66221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-1